            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x20,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Elise!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sophie. I'm sorry, I didn't notice you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "No, it's okay... What were you reading?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x5a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "A picture book. I drew it myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Wait... You can draw?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "That's right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Can I read it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's a little..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Is that a no?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's not finished yet. I was just checking how the story flows overall right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I still need to fill in a lot of details... That's why I don't want to show it to anyone now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I see, that's too bad... But why did you think about drawing a picture book?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "In the past, my grandfather converted a difficult book into a picture book, and read it to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's why I wanted to try making a picture book to read to children, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I'd be happy if they became more interested in reading books."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "So when that picture book is done, are you going to read it to children?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yes, of course."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I wonder how it'll turn out. I look forward to seeing it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. I'll do my best to meet your expectations."
        }
    ]
}